WEBVTT

00:02.120 --> 00:04.919
I need what I asked for...today.

00:05.960 --> 00:07.919
Or we'll pop round, pay Jenny a visit.

00:08.840 --> 00:09.799
Whatever he was doing,

00:09.920 --> 00:14.239
he didn't want anyone else to know
he was doing it. Tell me that's not dirty.

00:14.360 --> 00:18.439
He's making a decision on the roll
of a dice. Who to kill, when to kill...

00:18.560 --> 00:20.679
...whether or not to kill.

00:23.920 --> 00:25.279
Jenny.

00:30.360 --> 00:32.119
I'm sorry.

00:32.240 --> 00:34.239
I'm really, really sorry.

00:42.920 --> 00:46.639
- Justin, I can't talk tonight.
- We've got another one.

00:46.760 --> 00:49.039
It's started again.
There's two of them.

